{"tid":1604814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[前線討論] 革命唔係遊戲 係現場就攞勇氣出黎 齊上齊落","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T06:51:56.000Z","uid":217242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3439276860f808fd1769360802e1618e661103db","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:38:43.000Z","msg":"呢場戰爭開始咗3個幾月<br />\n初頭你地話要慢慢進化<br />\n我認為係言之有理 <br />\n因為香港人普遍係比較<span style=\"color: pink;\">善良</span><br />\n<br />\n但大家一齊經歷咗咁多場抗爭<br />\n由一開始舉黑旗都驚到依家好似家常便飯咁<br />\n由被動防守慢慢變向主動進攻<br />\n但係點解到依家仲係擺脫唔到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">速龍</span></strong></span></span>呢個陰影<br />\n<br />\n人數我地每次佔優 <br />\n但點解每一次都輸<br />\n點解每一次速龍衝<br />\n你地都要雞飛狗走！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解？！點解？！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>因為我地輸心態呀！</strong></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>因為我地輸心態呀！</strong></span></strong></span><br />\n我個人其實要求好簡單<br />\n大家可唔可以堅持個口號<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">齊上齊落</span></span></span></strong> <br />\n時代<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">*<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命</span></span>*</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我忍受唔住每一次想救人時<br />\n大家個個都跑走 得零星幾個係想幫手<br />\n拜託大家攞多d勇氣出黎！<br />\n佢地都係人都係會驚<br />\n只要企定防守慢慢退後拉人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地一定唔會咁大模廝樣衝入我地個防陣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日統一樓下前線手足係前邊專心頂緊防暴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">後排居然人數有優勢下都各自各跑走</span></span><br />\n最後搞到前線監生俾速龍切斷<br />\n然後就捉咗一大班人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實我係到想非常認真講一句</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong>落得場無論任何位置都<br />\n準備需要反抗 謝絕食花生！</strong></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你企後排唔代表完全交托<br />\n所以事情俾前排處理</span> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n真心拜託各位後排手足 <br />\n時刻保持警覺性準備反抗<br />\n唔係第一時間就做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>逃兵</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你地未有心理準備<br />\n唔該同最前排講聲<br />\n叫佢地快d撤退<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">每次個感覺其實真係非常唔好受</span><br />\n好似俾人當condom咁 有時真係感覺好灰<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線係前邊頂緊子彈<br />\n你地可唔可以反抗幫佢地頂住一陣</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">一齊防守一齊撤退 齊上齊落</span><br />\n<br />\n講事實係難聽<br />\n各位負評完唔該認真改善下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>我只不過希望各位10.1<br />\n可以平平安安大家一齊翻屋企</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHwnUhH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHwnUhH.jpg&h=517da8ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人無聊隨便亂講 <br />\n現實發生如有雷同 實屬巧合"},{"pid":"f3cdaa8ea4e359d0255a4e1618d1f06b7c1ab2f3","tid":1604814,"uid":311486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"今晚需要一個集氣大會。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604777</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"764f01c45cf1cde95771077632d5ce06bd43c6d2","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">希望各位可能再度覺醒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca2eec102445d4f3a9cce20e3b8bedd02b6f700","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"764f01c45cf1cde95771077632d5ce06bd43c6d2","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:40:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">希望各位可能再度覺醒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">*<span style=\"color: red;\">可以</span></span> Sor 唔係可能"},{"pid":"f85bf4280189d7bf7bcd9013a2570d5dd7ef5624","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">齊上齊落</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">勇敢面對</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反抗極權</span></span>"},{"pid":"b2f1cc239a7abc1fe4fd3c1a44e111645d8e453f","tid":1604814,"uid":171051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"只要齊心咩都做到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bIFIxpGNEbc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbIFIxpGNEbc&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1Tv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=56d986ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bIFIxpGNEbc</a>"},{"pid":"5d0118bd32a2ee4ede805a0ab49d959e02754a9a","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">速龍都係人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢唔係萬能</span></span><br />\n一齊set陣反抗 唔好再雞飛狗走喇<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">保護同伴</span> 人人有責</span></span>"},{"pid":"61d13930b92dfd8ffd452ef06cb81c8429d48b60","tid":1604814,"uid":64469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"［十一］暴風雨前夕 文宣組做野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604081</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5184080305fe4a89f891f96cbf806faa816ea83d","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2f1cc239a7abc1fe4fd3c1a44e111645d8e453f","tid":1604814,"uid":171051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"只要齊心咩都做到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bIFIxpGNEbc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbIFIxpGNEbc&d=eFPPjfgCRbiAcgLUcX%2Bp1Tv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=56d986ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bIFIxpGNEbc</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:48:54.000Z","msg":"無錯 我地進步咗的確係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如我所講 一到速龍衝出黎<br />\n大家好似真係見到鬼咁四散<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1934644ff4e4e5c39bba9de421dde181fdc8e81d","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">心態決定一切！</span></span><br />\n希望下次大家見到<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">速龍</span></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">無論身處咩位置都要真真正正防守</span><br />\n大嗌 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一齊打波！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">搶救同伴 人人有責</span></span>"},{"pid":"5a8dc7f8528c0be9e770a048cf0f3c6368421be9","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:06:51.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd10ae804df8c3e7022684d3cde544ae2a075296","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bdbb2cb7bb0bd3ed48cee8256930e1b7d2bdbc","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7b38818a92e45cd54f1908f46a90bb7e246d4cf","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c44ab690d35fde074342b95eff50b8253fa43e84","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479f576da286757fa50cc9f41de5159cc890bcfe","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cf693c801d21824ed341757eb0eed65f22ea20","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b480ad1bbb8d24927bd0c80c08c47a9d00ed3bbc","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f004f54ecaf6193acb4d5d4d0bf24557991e81f","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d364bd8424ceb9e4b21b0294a0cf6768dabdd1bc","tid":1604814,"uid":217242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" cl